### 5. üíß **Float Water Level Sensors (x3)**

* **Purpose**: Detects LOW level in water tank, nutrient tank, and mix tank.
* **Connections**: Digital input to GPIO 12, 13, and 14
* **Approx. Price**: ‚Çπ100 ‚Äì ‚Çπ150 each
* **Buy Link**: [Amazon India](https://www.amazon.in/s?k=water+level+sensor+float+switch)

---

### 6. ‚öóÔ∏è **Analog pH Sensor Module**

* **Purpose**: Measures acidity/alkalinity of the nutrient solution.
* **Analog Pin**: GPIO 34
* **Approx. Price**: ‚Çπ800 ‚Äì ‚Çπ1200
* **Buy Link**: [Amazon India](https://www.amazon.in/s?k=ph+sensor+module+arduino)

