### 9. üßÉ **5V DC Water Pumps (x3)**

* **Purpose**: Pump liquids from tanks:

  * Water pump (GPIO 18)
  * Nutrient pump (GPIO 19)
  * Mix pump (GPIO 21)
* **Voltage**: 5V DC
* **Approx. Price**: ‚Çπ300 ‚Äì ‚Çπ500 each
* **Buy Link**: [Amazon India](https://www.amazon.in/s?k=5v+dc+mini+water+pump)

---

### 10. üîÅ **Relay Module 2/4 Channel (x2)**

* **Purpose**: Controls DC pumps via digital GPIOs.
* **Input Voltage**: 5V
* **Control Pins**: GPIO 18, 19, 21
* **Approx. Price**: ‚Çπ120 ‚Äì ‚Çπ200 per module
* **Buy Link**: [Amazon India](https://www.amazon.in/s?k=relay+module+5v+arduino)

